PATHOLOGY: Study of disease and cause of death

Category: Medical
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

The study of disease and injury well enough to diagnose illness,
perform an autopsy, and determine a cause of death. Common training
for medical examiners, coroners, and Body Fixers who need to know
exactly what killed a patient, or what is still trying to.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

